  <h1>EchoIQ Privacy Policy</h1>

  <p>Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains how your information is used when you opt in for SMS messages.</p>

  <h2>SMS Consent</h2>
  <p>
    By opting in on our website, you agree to receive SMS appointment reminders, confirmations,
    and support messages from your dental office. You may withdraw your consent at any time by replying STOP.
  </p>

  <h2>Required Compliance Statement</h2>
  <p><strong>
    No mobile information will be shared with third parties/affiliates for marketing/promotional
    purposes. Information sharing to subcontractors in support services, such as customer service,
    is permitted. All other use case categories exclude text messaging originator opt-in data and
    consent; this information will not be shared with any third parties.
  </strong></p>

  <h2>Data Usage</h2>
  <p>Your information is used only for appointment-related communication.</p>

